Package org.eclipse.gef.mvc.fx.ui

package org.eclipse.gef.mvc.fx.ui
This package provides the bundle activator ( MvcFxUiBundle) as well as a Guice Module ( MvcFxUiModule) with default bindings for MVC.FX.UI.
